{
  "id": "indus_phase19_omnibus",
  "name": "Indus Phase-19 — omnibus (legacy migration)",
  "description": "Retroactive migration of scripts/phase19/omnibus.py. Runs Tier-1 (B/C/E) + Tier-3 (J/L) of the Phase-18 roadmap: 7-DoF / 6-DoF M77 projections, raw M77 OCR DoFs, top epistatic trigrams, per-inscription DoF distributions, spectral fingerprinting. Output: reports/phase19_omnibus.json.",
